OSI (open system Interconnection)

Level-7
* Application Layer
- User nearest layer
- HTTP, HTTPS, DNS, SSL
- User interface and network services
- All Application, web browser run on this.

Level-6
* Presentation Layer
- Data translation, encryption, compression

Level-5
* Session Layer
- Establisher and manages connections

Level-4
* Transport Layer
- TCP/UDP, error recovery, flow control (speed control)
- End to end data delivery

Level-3 
* Network Layer
- IP addressing and routing packets 

Level-2 
* Data Link Layer
- MAC addressing framing

Level-1
* Physical Layer
- physical transmission of bits
